trans-unit.source: Enables <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls or other server controls to contain collections of verbs.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller eller andre serverkontroller samlinger med verb.

trans-unit.source: A verb in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls is an action that a user can carry out in the user interface (UI).
trans-unit.target: Et verb i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller er en handling som en bruker kan utføre i brukergrensesnittet (UI).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a verb is represented in the UI by a clickable control such as a button, a link, or a menu item.
trans-unit.target: Et verb vanligvis er representert i Brukergrensesnittet ved å klikke kontrollen som en knapp, en kobling eller et menyelement.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control set provides standard verbs that are available by default to <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls and other server controls (such as custom, ASP.NET, and user controls) that can act like <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls when placed in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zones.
trans-unit.target: Webdeler kontrollen settet inneholder standard verb som er tilgjengelige som standard til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller og andre serverkontroller (for eksempel egendefinerte, ASP.NET, og brukeren styrer) som kan brukes som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollerer når er plassert i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>soner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Standard verbs include close, minimize, restore, delete, edit, and export.
trans-unit.target: Standard verb inkluderer Lukk, minimere, gjenoppretter, slette, redigere og Eksporter.

trans-unit.source: You can also create custom verbs for use with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> and server controls.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også opprette egendefinerte verb for bruk med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>og serverkontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The IWebActionable interface, with its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A> property, gives you a way to integrate custom verbs into your controls.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IWebActionable med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>egenskapen gir deg en måte å integrere egendefinerte verb i kontrollene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class implements the IWebActionable interface and implements its single property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klassen implementerer grensesnittet IWebActionable og implementerer egenskapen enkelt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: To add custom verbs to a control that inherits from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class, you must override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, add custom verbs to a collection, and return the collection.
trans-unit.target: Legge til egendefinert verb til en kontroll som arver fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klasse, må du overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen Legg til egendefinert verb i en samling og returnere samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The collection referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property contains only custom verbs; standard verbs are not included in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen henviser til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen inneholder bare egendefinerte verb; standard verb inkluderes ikke i denne samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The default return value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is `null`, because by default there are no custom verbs in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Standard returverdi av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen er `null`fordi som standard det finnes ingen egendefinerte verb i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Adding custom verbs to server controls that are not <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls requires one extra step.
trans-unit.target: Legger til egendefinert verb serverkontroller ikke <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller krever en ekstra trinn.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: In those cases, the controls must also implement the IWebActionable interface and implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: I slike tilfeller må kontrollene også implementere grensesnittet IWebActionable og implementere den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: After you have added custom verbs to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A> collection, the Web Parts control set automatically handles the other steps necessary to create and render the custom verbs.
trans-unit.target: Når du har lagt til egendefinerte verbene som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>samling, webdeler kontrollen automatisk behandler de andre trinnene som er nødvendig for å opprette og gjengi egendefinerte verbene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to a collection of custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Henter en referanse til en samling med egendefinerte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The Verbs property references a collection of custom verbs (if any) that are added to a verbs menu in the header of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> or other server control.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen verb refererer til en samling av egendefinerte verbene (Hvis noen) som er lagt til en verb meny i hodet til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>eller andre serverkontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The Verbs collection does not contain references to the standard <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb> objects provided with the Web Parts control set, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.CloseVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.DeleteVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.EditVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.RestoreVerb%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.MinimizeVerb%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen verb som ikke inneholder referanser til standard <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb>objektene som finnes i kontrollen webdeler satt, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.CloseVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.DeleteVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.EditVerb%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.RestoreVerb%2A>, eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.MinimizeVerb%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.MinimizeVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.RestoreVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.EditVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.DeleteVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.CloseVerb%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb>

trans-unit.source: Developers who want to add custom verbs to a custom control that derives from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class can simply override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A> property that the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class implements.
trans-unit.target: Utviklere som ønsker å legge til egendefinert verbene som en egendefinert kontrollere som er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klassen ganske enkelt kan overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A>egenskapen som det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klasse implementerer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Verbs%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Developers who want to add custom verbs to a user control, or a custom control that is not a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, must implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable> interface by providing an implementation of the Verbs property.
trans-unit.target: Utviklere som ønsker å legge til egendefinert verb en brukerkontroll eller en egendefinert kontroll som ikke er en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollere, må implementere den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable>grensesnittet ved hjelp av en implementering av egenskapen verb.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebActionable> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerbCollection"></xref> that contains custom <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerbCollection"> </xref> som inneholder egendefinerte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartVerb"> </xref> objekter.
